.. activecode:: turtle_3
    :author: DANIEL LEE
    :difficulty: 1.0
    :basecourse: thinkcspy
    :chapter: PythonTurtle
    :subchapter: Exercises
    :topics: PythonTurtle/Exercises
    :from_source: F

    Create a window with a background color. Create a herd of 4 colored 
    turtles that will draw 4 lines that will touch the edge of the window starting 
    in the center.
 
    +0.25 Use 3 more turtles per quadrant to draw from the center to the 
    edge. In each quadrant, be sure that each turtle has a unique color and are 
    equally spaced. 

    +0.25 Use 8 more turtles.

    ~~~~